---
title: Italian-Inspired Beyond Meat® Burgers with Caramelized Onions and Roasted Parmesan Potatoes
description: Get your napkins ready – this is one seriously juicy Beyond Meat® burger! We've loaded it with flavour, from the caramelized onions to the Parmesan mayo and garlicky roasted potatoes. Every bite will take you to your happy place.
